org.jboss.windup.reporting.freemarker

Class EffortPointsToCssClass

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jboss.windup.reporting.freemarker.EffortPointsToCssClass
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    freemarker.template.TemplateMethodModel, freemarker.template.TemplateMethodModelEx, freemarker.template.TemplateModel, WindupFreeMarkerMethod

    public class EffortPointsToCssClass
extends Object
implements WindupFreeMarkerMethod
    Converts from a number of effort points (story points) to a Css class.
    0 == info
    0-7 == warning
    8-13 == severe
    >13 == critical
    Author:
    Jesse Sightler
